Test Case ID: TC-006

Title:
Verify cart is empty after all items removed

Preconditions:
1. User is successfully signed in.
2. User in on the Product page with items in the cart.

Test Steps:
1. Remove all items from the cart by clicking the Remove button within the item description on items already in the cart

Expected Result:
1. No items are displayed in the cart.
2. Cart badge is no longer displayed.
3. Cart page indicates no items are present.
